Question
Represents a question within the quiz system.
QuestionController
The QuestionController class manages the CRUD operations for questions within quizzes.

The QuestionDTO class serves as a general data transfer object for questions, supporting different types of questions like text, slide, and true or false.
QuestionRepository
Manages storage and retrieval of Question entities.
QuestionService
Service class for handling operations related to quiz questions.
Quiz
Represents a quiz in the quiz system, including its title, associated questions, category, difficulty level, description, option to randomize question order, author information, and timestamps for creation and last update.

The QuizController class manages quiz-related operations within the application.

The QuizDTO class is a data transfer object that encapsulates the data of a quiz.

The QuizService class is responsible for managing quiz data within the application.
